## 📈 Sales Insights Dashboard – Nigeria

### 🔍 Overview

This dashboard analyzes sales performance across states, products, and channels.

### 💡 Key Insights

* Total Sales: 969.30M
* Top Selling Product: Keyboard
* Top Sales Channel: Online
* Highest Sales Month: July

### 📊 Features

* Interactive filters (Year, Month, Product, Channel)
* Monthly sales trend analysis
* State-wise sales comparison
* Product-wise distribution

### 🛠 Tools Used

* Power BI
* DAX
* Data Modeling
